      "descriptionOfEnablingFactor": "<p>Ghana implemented integrated landscape approaches for its national-level REDD+ strategy, enabled by global REDD+ discourse and funding. Other enabling factors include the World Bank's Forest Carbon Partnership Facility funding. </p>"
